	<message label="037" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Hier heb je wat <colour id="1" />snoep<colour id="65535" />!<delay40 /> <anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Dat zul je
